com.qualcomm.robotcore.robocol

Class Command

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qualcomm.robotcore.robocol.Command
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RobocolParsable, java.lang.Comparable<Command>, java.util.Comparator<Command>

    public class Command
extends java.lang.Object
implements RobocolParsable, java.lang.Comparable<Command>, java.util.Comparator<Command>
    Class used to send and receive commands

    These commands should be acknowledged by the receiver. The sender may resend the command repeatedly until it receives and acknowledgment from the receiver. The receiver should not reprocess repeated commands.
